'''爱情锁'''是一种能用以象征[[恋人|恋人]]间爱之永恒的锁。其可挂处，或[[桥梁|桥梁]]，或[[欄杆|栏楯]]，或門扉，或其他公共设施<ref name='bbc-rome'>{{cite news | first = Dana | last = Enulescu | title = Rome mayor in 'love padlock' row | date = 2007-03-01 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/6408635.stm | work = [[BBC|BBC]] | accessdate = 2011-08-19 | language = en | archive-date = 2017-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171222053333/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/6408635.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。有的锁厂会特制爱情锁，有的鎖上亦會有心型標誌<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url = http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2014-08/5116483.html|title = 塞尔维亚爱情桥上的南京锁：锁住爱情 祈祷和平|author = 叶璇|date = 2014-08-25|work = 环球网|accessdate = |archive-date = 2016-02-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160224145955/http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2014-08/5116483.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。挂锁前，恋人们常将自己名字写在锁上，并在挂锁后将钥匙抛离自己。自21世纪初，悬锁之风在世界范围内愈加兴盛<ref name="bbc-rome">{{cite news | first = Dana | last = Enulescu | title = Rome mayor in 'love padlock' row | date = 2007-03-01 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/6408635.stm | work = [[BBC|BBC]] | accessdate = 2011-08-19 | language = en | archive-date = 2017-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171222053333/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/6408635.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一些[[紀念建築物|紀念建築物]]亦为此特划悬锁区域。由于是举有损坏景观之果与导致事故之虞，一些地方亦对锁展开撤去作業。

== 悬锁歷史 ==
[[File:Most_Ljubavi_overview.jpg|200x200px]][[弗爾尼亞奇卡礦泉鎮|弗爾尼亞奇卡礦泉鎮]]<br/>至爱桥景|left]]
爱情锁之肇始，可溯至[[一战|一战]]以前[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]][[弗爾尼亞奇卡礦泉鎮|弗爾尼亞奇卡礦泉鎮]]的至爱桥（{{lang|sr|Most Ljubavi}}）。彼时，该镇女教師娜达（{{lang|sr|Nada}}）陷入与[[塞尔维亚王国|塞尔维亚王国]]军士官雷利亚（{{lang|sr|Relja}}）的热恋中。二人互誓永不变心。後雷利亚被征召前往[[希腊|希腊]]打仗，愛上一名來自[[克基拉島|克基拉島]]的女孩而不归。遠在故鄉的娜达得知后，心碎而死。當地女孩們為紀念這段故事，并表达对自己愛情之捍衛，開始將镌有自己與戀人姓名的鎖掛在當初之二人相遇的橋上，冀以防止對方變心。<ref name="vrnjackabanja.biz">{{cite web|title=Most ljubavi|url=http://www.vrnjackabanja.biz/mostljubavi.php|work=Vrnjacka Banja|publisher=www.vrnjackabanja.biz|accessdate=2010-10-06|language=sr|archive-date=2018-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180903175750/http://www.vrnjackabanja.biz/mostljubavi.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Ogrizović|first=Slobodan|title=Vrnjačka banja, najveće lečilište u Srbiji|url=http://www.b92.net/putovanja/destinacije/evropa.php?yyyy=2009&mm=04&dd=22&nav_category=823&nav_id=356735|accessdate=2010-10-06|newspaper=B92|date=2009-04-22|language=sr|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818183314/http://www.b92.net/putovanja/destinacije/evropa.php?yyyy=2009&mm=04&dd=22&nav_category=823&nav_id=356735|dead-url=no}}</ref>悬锁传统因[[二战|二战]]爆发而中断，又因塞尔维亚女诗人[[德珊卡·马克西莫维奇|德珊卡·马克西莫维奇]]笔下描绘这段爱情往事的诗歌《爱情祷告》（''{{lang|sr|Molitva za ljubav}}''）而再度受关注。观光季里，每日有大约五十人前来挂锁。<ref name=":0" />

[[File:Paris_Pont_des_Arts_upstream_rive_gauche_close-up.jpg|thumb]]艺术桥|left]]
21世纪初，悬锁现象现于欧洲他地。如在[[巴黎|巴黎]]，恋人们将名字镌在锁上，其中[[首字放大|首字用大字号]]，而后将之锁在桥梁栏楯上，并将钥匙投入[[塞纳河|塞纳河]]，作为不渝爱情的誓言。<ref name="ind-paris">{{cite news|first = Louisa|last = Long|title = Love-locks return to the bridges of Paris|date = 2011-06-06|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/lovelocks-return-to-the-bridges-of-paris-2293506.html|work = [[独立报|The Independent]]|accessdate = 2011-08-19|language = en|archive-date = 2011-08-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110810004225/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/lovelocks-return-to-the-bridges-of-paris-2293506.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>至于悬锁之愈加流行<ref name="欣传媒"/>，则是因[[意大利|意大利]]作家{{tsl|it|Federico Moccia|费德里科·莫恰}}2006年小説 《{{tsl|it|Ho voglia di te (romanzo)|愛是如此孩子氣}}》（''{{lang|it|Ho voglia di te}}''）及其2007年电影作品。<ref>{{Citation|author = Ian Fischer|date = 6 August 2007|title = In Rome, a New Ritual on an Old Bridge|journal = [[纽约时报|New York Times]]|url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/08/06/world/europe/06rome.html|accessdate = 2010-08-09|language = en|archive-date = 2011-08-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110829082254/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/08/06/world/europe/06rome.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="ponte">{{cite news|first = Justin|last = Demetri|title = The Bridge of Love in Rome|year = 2008|url = http://www.lifeinitaly.com/tourism/lazio/milvian-bridge.asp|work = Life in Italy .com|accessdate = 2011-08-19|language = en|archive-date = 2018-03-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180306021256/https://www.lifeinitaly.com/tourism/lazio/milvian-bridge.asp|dead-url = no}}</ref>作品中，男女主角在[[罗马|罗马]][[米爾維奧橋|米爾維奧橋]]（{{lang|it|Ponte Milvio}}）旁燈柱悬上其愛情鎖，继而將鑰匙丟入[[台伯河|台伯河]]，象徵從此刻起兩人永不分離，以堅定之愛情面對未來<ref name="欣传媒"/>。

==各地情锁==
[[臺灣|臺灣]][[豐原車站_(台灣)|豐原車站]]北侧天桥铁网亦有悬锁之俗，该桥亦随之被称为“心锁桥”。<ref name="东森">{{Cite news|url = http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120312/31110.htm|title = 豐原火車站心鎖橋獲保留　改立月台上|last = |first = |date = 2012-03-12|work = 东森新闻云|accessdate = |publisher = 東森新聞雲股份有限公司|archive-date = 2016-02-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160224105547/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20120312/31110.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>当地有一说法，称把对另一半的爱意写在锁上，然后天桥挂锁，就能将爱情牢牢锁在心房。且火车经过时会产生巨大[[磁场|磁场]]，愿望就能实现。<ref>{{cite web |authorlink= |author=Chang Jui-chen |year=2009 |url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2009/06/08/2003445646 |title='Wish lock' phenomenon attracts youth to Fengyuan |work= |publisher=[[台北時報|Taipei Times]] |accessdate=2009-12-06 |language=en |archive-date=2009-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611082346/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2009/06/08/2003445646 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此俗始于2003年。洎至2012年3月，此处已掛锁近萬，其形有大有小，其质有铜有木，亦有機車大鎖。随着鐵路高架化，此桥曾定于2013年拆除，网民遂于2012年2月发动联署呼籲保留，最终天桥拆除，而挂锁铁网转移到月台两端。<ref name="东森" />

